Kaya...

00:00:46.600 --> 00:00:48.080
ikaw ang aking kapatid, Da Xi?

00:00:51.880 --> 00:00:54.680
Ikaw si Tong Sheng mula sa Xuebao Group?

00:00:58.400 --> 00:01:00.160
Pagkatapos ng aksidente,

00:01:00.640 --> 00:01:03.280
ikaw ang tumira sa akin.

00:01:04.680 --> 00:01:05.720
tapos...

00:01:06.480 --> 00:01:07.600
naging Da Xi?

00:01:10.720 --> 00:01:11.760
At pagkatapos...

00:01:13.400 --> 00:01:15.120
ikaw ulit.

